snippet.title: Horse Riding ! Elsa & Anna toddlers - Horse Stable
snippet.description:
This toys dolls parody video shows ELSA & ANNA toddlers visiting Barbie's Horse Stable in a nice farm country area.
They are riding some cute horses and having a lot of fun with Barbie , Stacie and Chelsea ! The toddlers learn to ride horses.   Watch the video and enjoy their outdoors adventure !
